Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
savePreference(25.10)                                    savePreference(25.10)

Name
       savePreference - Saves the preference file

Syntax
       savePreference

       [-help]

       [-include_window_font]

       {[-directory {home current} | -file_name <PreferenceFileName>]}

       Saves the preference file.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and default in-
              formation for each savePreference parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man savePreference.

       -directory {home current}
              Specifies the directory path.

       -file_name <PreferenceFileName>
              Specifies the saved filename.

       -include_window_font
              Specifies the window and font settings.

       Related Information

              * getPreference

              * setPreference

              * For more information on setting preferences from the GUI,  see
                Set  Preference  form  in the View Menu chapter in the Innovus
                Menu Reference.

